                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’ai connu, Madame, une Dame,\nMoi vilain petit paysan,\nAussi grande de cœur et d’âme\nQue… la plus grande et… fine lame\nEt… pleine d’esprit… jugez-en."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Un soir, mon âme était complète,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Comme dit, après avoir bu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Le jeune homme qui fait la fête ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "De vrai, je n’avais plus ma tête,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "J’étais totalement fourbu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un soir, mon âme était complète,\nComme dit, après avoir bu,\nLe jeune homme qui fait la fête ;\nDe vrai, je n’avais plus ma tête,\nJ’étais totalement fourbu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "J’avais l’esprit un peu morose ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Je ne sais ce qui traversa",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Ma cervelle, pour quelle cause…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "« Comment, perdîtes vous… ta rose ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Oui, Madame, contez-nous ça. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’avais l’esprit un peu morose ;\nJe ne sais ce qui traversa\nMa cervelle, pour quelle cause…\n« Comment, perdîtes vous… ta rose ?\nOui, Madame, contez-nous ça. »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! que notre bêtise est grande !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Doux Jésus ! Amour de Sion !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Ma langue à vous se recommande…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Oui… car… pourquoi cette demande,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ou plutôt… cette question ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! que notre bêtise est grande !\nDoux Jésus ! Amour de Sion !\nMa langue à vous se recommande…\nOui… car… pourquoi cette demande,\nOu plutôt… cette question ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Comment perdîtes-vous… Ta rose ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et j’attendais, me tenant coi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Alors, tout doucement, sans pose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Comme on dit, hélas ! quelque chose",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "En songeant à n’importe quoi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comment perdîtes-vous… Ta rose ?\nEt j’attendais, me tenant coi.\nAlors, tout doucement, sans pose,\nComme on dit, hélas ! quelque chose\nEn songeant à n’importe quoi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "« Bien simplement. » répondit-elle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "N’est-ce pas céleste et charmant ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
